" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Camilla Simoncini"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/camilla-simoncini/">View all articles by Camilla Simoncini</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/03/two-men-show-antonio-pappano-e-lang-lang-allaccademia-di-santa-cecilia/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Two men show: Antonio Pappano e Lang Lang allAccademia di Santa Cecilia</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/03/teatro-dellopera-di-romamanon-lescaut/" rel="next">Teatro dell&#8217;Opera di Roma:&#8221;Manon Lescaut&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 3 comments</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-20672"> <article id="comment-20672" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/a60781249f30e231776f341e35061371?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">claudio tracchia</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/03/teatro-alla-scalail-trovatore/#comment-20672"><time datetime="2014-03-07T13:51:32+00:00">7 marzo 2014 at 13:51</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>D&#8217;accordo su tutto tranne che su Alvarez.La voce (almeno alla recita cui ho assistito)risuonava alquanto impicciolita e ridotta negli armonici,falsettante nelle mezzevoci.La AgrestA  sicuramente cantante di razza e di alta scuola.Suggerirei per in alcuni passi un accento un tantino pi vibrante.Ci vorrebbero per valorizzarla ulteriormente (ha gi tanto di suo)maestri come Serafin o Votto,ma dove li trovi pi?</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li><li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-20899"> <article id="comment-20899" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/21594275c27cacdbdb9ea6f7cb5b0415?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">Vittorio Baglieri</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/03/teatro-alla-scalail-trovatore/#comment-20899"><time datetime="2014-03-21T00:11:09+00:00">21 marzo 2014 at 00:11</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Non sono d&#8217;accordo su Alvarez: ha cantato bene il Miserere ma nelle altre parti la voce  usurata con qualche sprazzo interpretativo.. . Maria Agresta ha cantato ,nel complesso bene ,ma i filati sono stati smorzati, anche se ha sopperito con buoni legati. Condivido il giudizio su Franco Vassallo, meno quello<br /> su Ekaterina  Semenchuc(.  che ha saputo rendere il personaggio di Azucena con accenti drammatici. Spartana la direzione di Daniele Rustion. P.S.  e&#8217; la seconda volta che Rai 5 trasmette due volte lo stesso atto invece di procedere a mandare in onda quello successivo</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-21295"> <article id="comment-21295" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/e36bedc952aeb85fe22b6c59499074cd?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">Izolda</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/03/teatro-alla-scalail-trovatore/#comment-21295"><time datetime="2014-03-31T14:17:46+00:00">31 marzo 2014 at 14:17</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>I disagree with a critical opinion about performing of Mr. Alvarez &#8211; his sound had perfectly mild lines of legato, elegant passages during tonality changing, good controlled forte, clean, very sensitive mezzo voci and piano. Low register was too light and, may be, only in final act Argentinian tenor demonstrated perfectly rich, true Verdian colors of chiaroscuro. And in first act his sound was a little bit nasalize.  But mobility of voice, technical and breath control, quality of fioritura were excellent!  And, of course, good cantilena. Well, may be, there was less shining of hight notes, than earlier. But tessitura is perfectly suitable for his voice. And phrasing was good balanced, with harmonic combination of passion and sensitive, with some verismo tones. Mr. Alvarez is a true Manrico &#8211; I think, it&#8217;s very difficult (almost impassible) to find better performer of Verdi repertoire today, than Alvarez with such rare combination of beautiful timbre and good vocally style.<br /> Agresta is perfectly as Violetta Valery, but delicate coloratura and shining high notes is not enough for rich dramatic role of Leonora. Low register was very weak and structure of timbre&#8217;s shadows was lyrically light, without  dramatical size. Vocal lines of Leonora&#8217;s role have to be more rich and deep. The weakest performer of the cast is Semenchuk &#8211; problems with high register and terribly forced low notes without smooth mezzo colors.</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li></ol><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2014/03/teatro-alla-scalail-trovatore/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sar pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required=\'true\' required=\'required\' /></p><p class="comment-form-email"><label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="email" name="email" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="100" aria-describedby="email-notes" aria-required=\'true\' required=\'required\' /></p><p class="comment-form-url"><label for="url">Sito web</label> <input id="url" name="url" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="200" /></p><p class="form-submit"><input name="submit" type="submit" id="submit" class="submit" value="Commento all&#039;articolo" /> <input type=\'hidden\' name=\'comment_post_ID\' value=\'69832\' id=\'comment_post_ID\' /> <input type=\'hidden\' name=\'comment_parent\' id=\'comment_parent\' value=\'0\' /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="akismet_comment_nonce" name="akismet_com